## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not fully represent the diversity of healthcare settings and practices. Additionally, the data is drawn from studies with varying methodologies, which could affect the comparability of results. Further research with a broader scope and more standardized methods would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.

